QuestData.Title: Back to the Tenebrous Cavern
QuestData.Description: YOU MUST RETURN... TO... THE TENEBROUS CAVERN. ERUNAK STONESPEAKER AWAITS... YOU WITHIN.$B$BI DIE NOW....
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Erunak Stonespeaker at the Tenebrous Cavern in Vashj'ir.
QuestData.RewardText: Hello again, $c.$B$BI felt L'ghorek die. A shame that such a magnificent being is gone.$B$BIf we do not assist Neptulon, we will all meet the same fate.
